{
  "texts": [
    "Compliance with privacy laws, such as the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), is critical and requires robust frameworks for data protection, anonymization, and informed consent.",
    "Moreover, industries must promote transparency regarding data usage, providing consumers with clear explanations of how their data will be utilized and ensuring they retain control over their personal information.",
    "Implementing privacy-preserving AI techniques, such as federated learning, represents a viable strategy for addressing these regulatory challenges.",
    "(6) Rapidly Evolving Technology Landscape.",
    "The fast-paced evolution of AI methodologies presents both opportunities and challenges."
  ]
}